  <brief_title>Peripheral Nerve Block (Femoral - Sciatic - Obturator) Versus General Anesthesia for Arthroscopic ACL Repair</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Femoral - Sciatic - Obturator Nerve Block vs General Anesthesia in Combination With Continuous or Bolus Femoral Nerve Block for Arthroscopic ACL Repair Regarding the Time of Patient Mobilasation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
